From 022cff7d7e364d6458923a2ff3fadbe96fb738ce Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Li Zhou <li.zhou@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 25 Dec 2018 22:48:48 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 06/12] mm: replace get_user_pages_unlocked() write/force
 parameters with gup_flags

commit c164154f66f0c9b02673f07aa4f044f1d9c70274 upstream.

This removes the 'write' and 'force' use from get_user_pages_unlocked()
and replaces them with 'gup_flags' to make the use of FOLL_FORCE
explicit in callers as use of this flag can result in surprising
behaviour (and hence bugs) within the mm subsystem.

Signed-off-by: Lorenzo Stoakes <lstoakes@gmail.com>
